TITLE: Defining MaxAge Field for CORS in Go
DESCRIPTION: Defines the MaxAge field for CORS configuration in Gateway API. This field indicates the duration (in seconds) for the client to cache the results of a 'preflight' request. It has a default value of 5 seconds and must be at least 1 second.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/gateway-api/blob/main/geps/gep-1767/index.md#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
// +optional
// +kubebuilder:default=5
// +kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1
MaxAge int32 `json:"maxAge,omitempty"`
```

